data.description: This charming 5-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom property features recent interior enhancements, including freshly painted interiors and a new vanity, infusing modernity and style into the home. The kitchen boasts new appliances—a garbage disposal and dishwasher—as well as a pot filler and updated flooring, enhancing its functionality and aesthetics. The property offers a solar system, water softener, and recently replaced doors and windows, providing added convenience and energy efficiency. The HVAC, water heater, and roof were installed in 2020, ensuring comfort. Nestled in a vibrant area with nearby amenities like portsmouth naval hospital, gas stations, supermarkets, and diverse dining options, it ensures easy access to daily essentials. Enjoy parks, recreation centers, and proximity to Portsmouth Fire Station 7 for community engagement and outdoor activities. $30k solar loan to be assumed. Don't miss the opportunity to explore this convenient and inviting home!
